Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.11,0:00:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到羅德斯島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.71,0:00:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼緊接著\N就請觀賞第二部份吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.92,0:00:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,~歡迎來到羅德斯島~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.86,0:00:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗噗噗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.09,0:00:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂~各位啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.33,0:00:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是完全迷路了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.23,0:00:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事呀，這個迷宮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.73,0:00:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!迷宮!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.47,0:00:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有迷宮的學校是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.70,0:00:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷宮(男女)同校!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.97,0:00:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，接的漂亮，潘恩\N你的技巧又進步了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.81,0:00:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝誇獎，陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.98,0:00:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在幹什麼呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.99,0:00:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，該怎麼辦啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.48,0:00:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去不就回不了地上了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.62,0:00:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是根據在街上打聽到的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.72,0:00:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這裡藏有支配的王錫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.06,0:00:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種窮鄉僻壤的地下迷宮裡\N才不可能有支配的王錫呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.13,0:00:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會只是捕風捉影吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.30,0:00:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西莉絲!這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.10,0:01:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇!別嚇我啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.64,0:01:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.04,0:01:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來像是寶箱\N而且有寫什麼字呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.74,0:01:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要突然冒出來呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.64,0:01:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來好像是古代語呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.55,0:01:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫了些什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.41,0:01:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些地方不擦就看不懂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.67,0:01:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ㄒ○ㄧ的ㄨㄤ○ㄑ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.82,0:01:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市內的王國…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.39,0:01:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主持的蠻橫…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.22,0:01:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話劇的王角…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.03,0:01:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配的王錫!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.96,0:01:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就真的有了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.00,0:01:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，快打開來看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.14,0:01:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭，原來是棺材啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.11,0:01:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛，這個腳○型的很厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.44,0:01:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這到底為何會寫成\N支配的王錫呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.67,0:01:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了!明白了!我知道了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.45,0:01:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體的○腳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.08,0:01:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.75,0:01:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.39,0:01:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得再看喔
